cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this dataset, please cite it as below."
title: "OpenRouter Uptime: an independent availability and data-policy registry for OpenRouter models"
abstract: >-
  An independent, hourly, git-timestamped registry of the availability of every
  model on OpenRouter and each of its inference providers, together with each
  provider's data policy (training, prompt retention, terms of service). Raw API
  responses are archived as ground truth; tidy tables are mirrored to HuggingFace
  and Kaggle.
type: dataset
authors:
  - given-names: Wenbin
    family-names: Wu
repository-code: "https://github.com/dthinkr/openrouter-uptime"
url: "https://github.com/dthinkr/openrouter-uptime"
keywords:
  - openrouter
  - large language models
  - uptime
  - infrastructure
  - AI governance
  - time series
